H1: quote Filter

H2: Interface

!filter_interface "quote"

H2: Description

The {{quote}} filter is used to format a quotation.
This typically implies:

* for [[PostScript]], the text is italics and indented from
  both margins
* for [[HTML]], the text is given an appropriate style.

